item.title: Test 1 Information
item.description: The first test, on Wednesday March 24, will be released at the beginning of the class session (9:40 AM) through a Blackboard announcement. The test is designed to take one hour. You may complete it during the class session, or you may submit it later in the day. Tests submitted any time on March 24 will be on time. Submit through the upload link at the course Blackboard site > Tests > Test 1.
